lillipee
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:A porridge or gruel made of flour (occas. sugar), or grain boiled;  cf also stirabout.
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
